"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-sport-other-sport-trans-women-banned-olympics-female-events\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"GB NEWS ByEd Griffiths, Published: 10/11/2025 Updated: 10/11/2025 Olympic sports had the power individually to decide whether transgender women could compete with reduced testosterone levels Transgender women are reportedly set to be banned from competing in female competitions.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Transgender women\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trans_woman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"GB NEWS ByEd Griffiths\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 22}, {\"ngram\": \"10/11/2025 Olympic sports\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 94}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender women\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 143}, {\"ngram\": \"reduced testosterone levels\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 190}, {\"ngram\": \"female competitions\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committeeis set to announce a ban early next year.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The International Olympic Committeeis\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"a ban\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It follows a science-based review of evidence on the permanent physical advantages of being born male.Previously, Olympic sports had the power individually to decide whether transgender women could compete with reduced testosterone levels.TRENDINGStoriesVideosYour SayThis will now be changed, according to The Times.Athletics and swimming already have bans in place for athletes who have been through male puberty, but many events have not implemented the changes.IOC president Kirsty Coventry is likely to have been behind the changes after she repeatedly affirmed her desire to \\\"protect the female category\\\".Dr Jane Thornton, the IOC's medical and scientific director, presented the review's findings to members at a meeting in Lausanne last week, according to the report.Transgender women are set to be banned from competing in female competitions, according to reports|GETTYOne source told the publication: \\\"It was a very scientific, factual and unemotional presentation which quite clearly laid out the evidence.\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kirsty Coventry\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kirsty_Coventry\"}, {\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Thornton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jane Thornton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Thornton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jane_Thornton\"}, {\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1000, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.755923737446058e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lausanne\", \"score\": 0.9999999999861302, \"rank\": 1.3744821605604485e-11, \"text\": \"Lausanne\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lausanne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lausanne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a science-based review\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 397}, {\"ngram\": \"evidence\", 